desc: The Uk’s premier one-stop Farm to Fork producer of award-winning, welfare assured, sustainable lamb and beef. All of our lamb and beef is provenance assured and sourced from within the Yorkshire Dales or Lake District National Park. World-class Master Butcher ensures your receive the finest cuts direct to your door.
